{"tid":1302471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚七點正，麥小姐追悼晚會","createTime":"2019-07-10T03:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T11:59:40.000Z","uid":134134,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"0d8fac30c3fca14ab29eda0ac81554c539300f50","tid":1302471,"uid":134134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YzPMPNk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYzPMPNk.png&h=22b77e6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n時間：七時正至十時半<br />\n地點：中環愛丁堡廣場<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以抽空出席一下<br />\n其實我都唔知係好定唔好，近排連登，甚至社會洋溢着歡樂嘅氣氛，少咗之前嘅壓力同緊張感。我知道長期拉得咁緊並唔係一件好事。麥小姐正正係因情緒太壓抑，心中條弦拉得太緊，而離開咗我哋。但我都希望大家可藉著麥小姐，回想返起呢場運動陰暗嘅一面。因為我深信，如果要喺抗爭嘅路上向成功嘅方向前進，太陽與影子缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>7.10</strong> - <ins>TVB港姐</ins> - <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1300556\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/1300556</a><br />\n<strong>7.10</strong> - <ins>麥小姐追思會</ins> ＠ 中環愛丁堡廣場 - 19:00~22:30<br />\n<strong>7.11</strong> - <ins>梁烈士公眾告別禮</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8Cu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=dd8bfe07\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n<strong>7.11</strong> - <ins>油尖旺區議會夢遊</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8Cu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=1db34506\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/ytm_dc711</a><br />\n<strong>7.12</strong> - <ins>光復港大 守衛我城</ins> - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2S6Lw1T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2S6Lw1T&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8Cu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=d8ae6d54\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2S6Lw1T</a><br />\n<strong>7.13</strong> - <ins>光復上水</ins> - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/32eEvRm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32eEvRm&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8Cu2we